<resolution-body style="multiple-resolved-clause" id="H38B1016DEEE547C1A42628A93703C7B6"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="H33FEFABC2A304457817A3F616FB663D6"><text>That </text></section> <section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="H034D7A58A7DE4B3980F4494B81C6E801"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">the House has heard with profound sorrow of the death of the Honorable Lindsey Graham, a Senator from the State of South Carolina.</text></section>
<section id="H24399F6734FE4F348F0B3AAB68740230" section-type="resolved"><text>That the Clerk communicate these resolutions to the Senate and transmit a copy thereof to the family of the deceased.</text></section> <section id="H6AC9190DB0554614A5DB556F255B8622" section-type="resolved"><text>That when the House adjourns today, it adjourn as a further mark of respect to the memory of the deceased.</text></section> 
</resolution-body> 
